channel.title: RuneScapes Cache
channel.description:
While messing around watching youtube video's I found one about the new slayer master on runescape, and the video was from December, way before the update took place.
Link of the new Wise Old Man: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=raStb029gZs
Now, is it possible(I don't know how to do it) To go into RuneScapes Cache and go threw to see if you can possibly find a Npc with the new skillcape on it? Since it appears Jagex is already planning for the future by adding this stuff in already.
